Beijing Lier Plans 1.4 Billion Yuan Polysilicon Project in Henan

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-07-12T23:24:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-12/beijing-lier-plans-1-4-billion-yuan-polysilicon-project-in-henan.html
Beijing Lier High-temperature
Materials Co. plans to invest 1.4 billion yuan in a polysilicon
project in central  China ’s Henan province, the company said in a
statement to Shenzhen’s stock exchange.  The project will have an annual output of 5,000 tons, the
statement said. Construction of the project is estimated to be
completed by July 2012, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  